   N_Q_HEADS=64 KV_HEADS=4 HEAD_DIM=128 GQA=16  (q [M][heads][hd], KV shared across M)

correctness vs CPU fp32 (M=1, 3 heads): max_abs_err = 1.472e-08  -> PASS (tol 1e-2)

