  8    8          4096                    192.08      24.01   4.291
  16   4          4096                    370.35      23.15   8.274

  HEADLINE: if us(M=8)/us(M=1) ~ 1.0 the K2 k-scaling is gone (occupancy-fill worked) and the
  spec verify forward goes flat -> the 840-1000 path is unblocked.  Compare to the per-warp-loop
  tp8_k2_partial_mq which measured 1.5x at M=8.  (Next: wire the winner into decode_step_tp8.cu.)
